              <span id="reviewTextContainer1128495480" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1885643972244392783">This has been a great study and discussion book. It is very readable and organized in a way that prompts study and reflection. You can tell he has been an excellent teacher. I especially liked the way he used personal and modern experiences along with scriptural ones to make his points. This made it more interesting and easier to absorb the principles. This has been one of the best books I have read with the study group because it fostered so many deep and personal discussions.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


