        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2203411347" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13187318990996615510">Had a bit of a hard time getting into the book but once I did, it was very helpful. I need to go through it again to gain a better understanding of what the author was saying. It took me a while to get through the book because of things that were going on in my life plus I wasn&apos;t really understanding the first half of the book as much as the 2nd half, for some reason. He has 3 other books in the Divine Guidance series. </span>
