<div id="review_2532639332" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2532639332" />
    <a title="Sara" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3501058-sara"><img alt="Sara" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1269665212p2/3501058.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2532639332?book_show_action=true">Sep 23, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sara" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sara" href="/user/show/3501058-sara">Sara</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3501058-sara?shelf=audio">audio</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3501058-sara?shelf=religious">religious</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2532639332" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13254282691069089678">Lund is a powerful author, with a strong pedigree in religious education and study. This is one of my favorite works of his.<br/><br/>Written with an LDS slant, Hearing the Voice of the Lord is useful for any Christian seeking to better understand the Holy Spirit, how it works, and how we improve on this gift. <br/><br/>Clearly outlined, using scriptural references, heavy annotation and personal anecdotes, I almost didn&apos;t want it to end.<br/><br/>Truly inspiring and compelling. I learned a lot.</span>
  <span id="freeText13254282691069089678" style="display:none">Lund is a powerful author, with a strong pedigree in religious education and study. This is one of my favorite works of his.<br /><br />Written with an LDS slant, Hearing the Voice of the Lord is useful for any Christian seeking to better understand the Holy Spirit, how it works, and how we improve on this gift. <br /><br />Clearly outlined, using scriptural references, heavy annotation and personal anecdotes, I almost didn't want it to end.<br /><br />Truly inspiring and compelling. I learned a lot.</span>
  <a data-text-id="13254282691069089678" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


