        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2632940988" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15757659725406783997">I’ve read Lund’s fiction works before but this is the first time I’ve read a book of his in which he teaches and writes about doctrine. He does not disappoint. <br/><br/>This is an invaluable resource in understanding, improving, and benefiting from personal revelation. Thorough, but not boring. Highly recommended for all members of the Church. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


