<span id="freeTextContainer15638795664972496422">This book was so helpful to me. Its wise insights have been helping me to live a better, happier, more effective life. I recommend it to anyone, but especially to fellow members of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints. Even though it was written 13 years ago, it pairs well with President Nelson&apos;s recent counsel about the importance and urgent need of personal revelation in our lives.</span>
